# Canonical portal URLs (EA / CTP)

## QUARANTINED — never recommend, never link, never open as CTP

| Status | URL |
|--------|-----|
| **QUARANTINED** | `https://efficiencyarchitects.online/ctp-intake` |
| **QUARANTINED** | `https://efficiencyarchitects.online/ctp-intake/*` |
| **QUARANTINED** | Any `/ctp-intake` path on ea-payments apex |

This is the Discover wizard alias mislabeled as CTP. It is **not** Consider the Possibilities™ intake. Agents that suggest this URL are wrong. Production redirects it away.

## Production — correct CTP surfaces

| Purpose | URL |
|---------|-----|
| **CTP Magnifi story entry (preferred public entry)** | https://efficiencyarchitects.online/consider/selena |
| **Codex Operational MRI / CTP on CRA (when restored)** | https://cc.efficiencyarchitects.online/ctp |
| Same CRA deploy (when restored) | https://efficiency-architects.vercel.app/ctp |
| CRA source | nested `efficiency-architects/efficiency-architects` → `OperationalMRI.jsx` |
| Legacy MRI quiz on CRA | https://cc.efficiencyarchitects.online/operational-mri |
| **Client portal login** | https://efficiencyarchitects.online/portal/login |
| **EA portal home** | https://efficiencyarchitects.online/portal/ea |
| **Demo CTP workspace** | https://efficiencyarchitects.online/portal/demo-client/ctp |
| **One-click demo session** | https://efficiencyarchitects.online/api/auth/demo-enter |

Funnel: `/consider/{slug}` → portal CTP workspace after provision.  
`/buy` is Website + Portal Starter — not CTP intake.  
`/discover` is the Discover wizard product — **not** CTP branding; do not call it CTP.

Also OK (portal host): `https://portal.efficiencyarchitects.online/...`

## Wrong surfaces (do not treat as CTP)

- `www.efficiencyarchitects.online` — often old Growth Portal / wrong Vercel project
- `cc.efficiencyarchitects.online` root when it serves NextStepsPro LaunchPad (not EA CTP)
- Next Steps Pro “Portal unavailable” LaunchPad — not this app
- **`/ctp-intake` on efficiencyarchitects.online — QUARANTINED**

## Local

- Login: http://localhost:3000/portal/login
- Prefer password sign-in when `RESEND_API_KEY` / OTP is not wired
- Do not use `/api/auth/demo-enter` locally if it redirects to production apex
- `/ctp-intake` locally redirects to `/consider/selena` (quarantine)

## Local env needed for email OTP

`AIRTABLE_API_KEY` and `RESEND_API_KEY` in `.env.local` (restart `npm run dev` after adding).
